Vivek K. Jayaraman



Mr. Vivek K. Jayaraman is Chief Commercial Officer at Cerus Corp. Mr. Jayaraman was previously employed as Head-Media Relations, VP-Global Sales & Marketing by Trivascular Technologies, Inc., Vice President-Global Sales & Marketing by TriVascular, Inc., and Vice President-Commercial Operations by Trivascular2, Inc. He received his undergraduate degree from the University of Michigan and an MBA from The Wharton School of the University of Pennsylvania.



